1. *Sediš* na mojoj stolici. (You are sitting on my chair.)
2. Kada *sediš*, drži leđa pravo. (When you sit, keep your back straight.)
3. *Sediš* preko puta mene. (You are sitting across from me.)
4. *Sediš* tako neugodno, da li te nešto boli? (You are sitting so uncomfortably, is something hurting you?)
5. Dok *sediš*, ne igraj se sa stolicom. (While you sit, don't play with the chair.)
6. *Sediš* u prvom redu uvek. (You always sit in the front row.)
7. Kada sam došao, već si *sediš* tu. (When I arrived, you were already sitting here.)
8. Molim te, *sediš* mirno i slušaj me. (Please, sit still and listen to me.)
9. *Sediš* na ivici kreveta, da li si dobro? (You are sitting on the edge of the bed, are you okay?)
10. *Sediš* u zadnjoj klupi, ali to ne znači da manje učiš. (You sit in the back row, but that doesn't mean you study less.)